00:12:38.250 --> 00:12:40.290
It obviously fit the
context of what people

00:12:40.290 --> 00:12:41.860
were interested in at the time.

00:12:41.860 --> 00:12:44.110
But we had a role
in help shaping it.

00:12:44.110 --> 00:12:46.600
So 100 years later, we've
come to realize, hey,

00:12:46.600 --> 00:12:49.570
if we can help people understand
why it's important to drink

00:12:49.570 --> 00:12:53.370
orange juice or why it's
important to save their money

00:12:53.370 --> 00:12:56.300
