01:05:01.800 --> 01:05:02.300
-OK.

01:05:02.300 --> 01:05:05.266
Well, thank you so much.

01:05:07.850 --> 01:05:09.000
Wow.

01:05:09.000 --> 01:05:11.320
This was like a dream for me.

01:05:11.320 --> 01:05:13.980
I mean, all these panels
of knowledgeable people.

01:05:13.980 --> 01:05:17.840
Basically I was given license to
want to learn about this topic.

01:05:17.840 --> 01:05:22.460
And we were able to pick these
very thoughtful panelists.

01:05:22.460 --> 01:05:28.250
And I can't begin to express
my gratitude towards them.

01:05:28.250 --> 01:05:29.460
We're just lucky.

01:05:29.460 --> 01:05:31.290
Thank you.

01:05:31.290 --> 01:05:31.810
Let's see.

01:05:31.810 --> 01:05:35.310
