01:05:59.790 --> 01:06:03.870
I think that's the
right metaphor.

01:06:03.870 --> 01:06:08.040
So Alison Franklin,
Jessica [INAUDIBLE],

01:06:08.040 --> 01:06:13.510
Maura Madden, Paul Baron, and
