01:06:17.010 --> 01:06:17.570
happen.

01:06:17.570 --> 01:06:20.810
And I am incredibly
grateful to her.

01:06:20.810 --> 01:06:23.850
So to summarize, I
don't think I can really

01:06:23.850 --> 01:06:25.730
put it all into thought.

01:06:25.730 --> 01:06:27.200
So what I'm going
to do is just use

01:06:27.200 --> 01:06:30.350
some of the quotes that were
memorable that I wrote down,

01:06:30.350 --> 01:06:32.410
and hopefully it won't
take up too much time.

01:06:32.410 --> 01:06:35.110
But these were quotes that
came out of people's mouths,

01:06:35.110 --> 01:06:38.994
both in the comedy
session and today.

01:06:38.994 --> 01:06:40.660
And they were just
things that I flagged

01:06:40.660 --> 01:06:44.080
that seemed to, in a sense,
encapsulate the conference.

01:06:44.080 --> 01:06:47.560
So from last night--
"women are fed

01:06:47.560 --> 01:06:49.920
so many contradictory
messages that all you can do

01:06:49.920 --> 01:06:55.820
is be a robot." "Tragedy
plus time equals comedy."

01:06:55.820 --> 01:06:58.200
"Language reifies binary.

01:06:58.200 --> 01:07:01.150
This is sufficient
grounds for change."

01:07:01.150 --> 01:07:04.260
"Reality is constructed
with language."

01:07:04.260 --> 01:07:08.020
"Women have natural
power." "Matrilineal tribes

01:07:08.020 --> 01:07:09.980
are more accepting of
third and fourth genders

01:07:09.980 --> 01:07:12.290
than patriarchal tribes."

01:07:12.290 --> 01:07:17.430
"There is no trans equivalent
of the Academie Francaise

01:07:17.430 --> 01:07:19.610
in regard to language change.

01:07:19.610 --> 01:07:24.000
It's too important to
rush." "Be shamelessly

01:07:24.000 --> 01:07:27.320
flexible with your
language." "If I am passing,

01:07:27.320 --> 01:07:33.970
someone else is failing." "When
we center the marginalized,

01:07:33.970 --> 01:07:36.630
we become liberated."
"Get closer

01:07:36.630 --> 01:07:40.160
to a multi-layered self."

01:07:40.160 --> 01:07:42.470
Echoing another
thought-- "Women are

01:07:42.470 --> 01:07:46.730
faced with impossible
images in media."

01:07:46.730 --> 01:07:50.010
"Allow yourself to
embrace uncertainty."

01:07:50.010 --> 01:07:52.620
"An opinion is the short
skirt of the internet."

01:07:52.620 --> 01:07:55.040
I like that one.

01:07:55.040 --> 01:08:00.050
"The rise of the word
misandry in social media."

01:08:00.050 --> 01:08:05.830
"Communication is
incredibly contextual."

01:08:05.830 --> 01:08:08.440
From a questioner-- "If
I get policed by men,

01:08:08.440 --> 01:08:12.550
I get policed by men, but
secretly supported by women."

01:08:12.550 --> 01:08:16.660
"Women, no matter what they
do, it's the wrong choice."

01:08:16.660 --> 01:08:19.910
"If your uterus is
functioning, your brain can't."

01:08:19.910 --> 01:08:22.399
Ironically.

01:08:22.399 --> 01:08:24.490
The term "role ricochet"
which was made up

01:08:24.490 --> 01:08:25.779
for this conference.

01:08:25.779 --> 01:08:26.336
Thanks, Mary.

01:08:29.399 --> 01:08:32.680
"That is way sexier, a
gorilla playing on drums."

01:08:32.680 --> 01:08:34.079
Again, context is everything.

01:08:36.600 --> 01:08:39.319
"A dad man, this
makes me insane.

01:08:39.319 --> 01:08:43.359
So when I go to work, does
this make me a mom dad?"

01:08:43.359 --> 01:08:47.640
And the one that Mary had
to tell me to shut up.

01:08:47.640 --> 01:08:52.229
"Look at what this does
for resting bitch face."

01:08:52.229 --> 01:08:54.859
In terms of run like a girl--
"It means run as fast as you

01:08:54.859 --> 01:09:00.370
can." "She's not doing better
because she shouts too much."

01:09:00.370 --> 01:09:03.670
"We're not allowed to
laugh too big or too loud."

01:09:03.670 --> 01:09:05.850
And I guess I'll
end with this one.

01:09:05.850 --> 01:09:08.279
"Are we capable of saying
what we really mean?"

01:09:08.279 --> 01:09:10.170
That sounds like a
good one to end it on.

01:09:10.170 --> 01:09:12.880
So thank you so
much for attending.

01:09:12.880 --> 01:09:14.560
You've been a great audience.

01:09:14.560 --> 01:09:17.686
And I think it's been
a great set of panels.

01:09:17.686 --> 01:09:19.274
And I've learned
an amazing amount.

01:09:19.274 --> 01:09:20.820
So I'm just grateful for all.

